products.name: Gardénia
products.desc: The lush, gardenia-infused fragrance Coco Chanel created in 1924 was an ode to the flower closest in character to her beloved camellia. Its storied heritage is further elevated by this grand presentation —— a limited-edition, deluxe grand flacon; a treasure for Parfum connoisseurs and fragrance collectors alike.
